{"tid":404655,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（一拳Mario) Mario 變成一拳超人？過關易過借火","createTime":"2017-09-18T09:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T11:23:26.000Z","uid":22869,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f54b3658d908e24bc5e9a3956465e1d3a4854b9","tid":404655,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/172019_5b4c329c71c0980dd746e5413e0e3dd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F172019_5b4c329c71c0980dd746e5413e0e3dd3.jpg&h=a916d088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMario 可以説是史上最強的水管工，一次又一次經歷各種超強關卡救公主，十分厲害。說到 Mario 最特別的地方，就是擁有很多條命，跳得很高，而且可以隨時吃蘑菇、星星變身。雖然如此，Mario 十分脆弱，不小心碰一碰都會死。如果，Mario 擁有一拳超人那麽強的力量，又會變成怎樣？<br />\n<br />\n國外 Youtube 頻道「Level UP Gaming」就做了一條動畫，當 Mario 擁有超人能力，就再也不用跑跑跳跳去過關了。見到有門就直接衝進去，有怪物就直接將所有裝置抛去岩漿，完全不用跳起躲開，連怪物都怕了他。可是這樣的 Mario 大叔好像強過頭了，打 Boss 超輕鬆，完美沒有緊張感。另外，作者還在片中放了小彩蛋，片中隱藏了路易吉、耀西以及奇諾比奧，大家有發現到嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1901892/Mario%20%E8%AE%8A%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E6%8B%B3%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9F%E9%81%8E%E9%97%9C%E6%98%93%E9%81%8E%E5%80%9F%E7%81%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1901892%2FMario%2520%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%258B%25B3%25E8%25B6%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25BC%259F%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2598%2593%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%2580%259F%25E7%2581%25AB&d=Y8qSumg6seHukszPxWBdZeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=0182b63d\" target=\"_blank\">http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1901892/Mario%20%E8%AE%8A%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E6%8B%B3%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9F%E9%81%8E%E9%97%9C%E6%98%93%E9%81%8E%E5%80%9F%E7%81%AB</a>"},{"pid":"5b21df3153e6bd4f11b03a5d4490619a589303ca","tid":404655,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1Sw8ITcq8iI\" data-sr-url=\"http